<!-- Project Overview -->
<section class="container mb-5">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-8">
            <h2 class="section-title">Project Overview</h2>
            <p>This project conducts a comprehensive customer segmentation analysis for an e-commerce business. I have used advanced clustering techniques, RFM analysis and ML techniques.</p>
            
            
            <h3 class="mt-4">Business Objectives</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Identify distinct customer segments based on behavior and purchasing patterns</li>
                <li>Develop targeted marketing strategies and personalized experiences for each segment</li>
                <li>Create a recommendation system to predict products of interest for different customer groups</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-4">
            <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title">Technologies Used</h5>
