                        <figcaption class="text-muted mt-2">2D visualization of product embeddings from model.</figcaption>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    
    <!-- Customer Lifetime Value -->
    <div class="card visualization-card mb-5">
        <div class="card-body">
            <h4 class="card-title">4. Customer Lifetime Value Analysis</h4>
            <p class="card-text">I developed a comprehensive CLV model that incorporates purchase frequency, average order value, and customer retention probability to estimate the future value of each customer segment.</p>
            <div class="text-center">
                <img src="static/images/customer_segmentation/customer_ltv_analysis.png" alt="Customer Lifetime Value Analysis" class="img-fluid viz-img" style="max-width: 800px;">
                <figcaption class="text-muted mt-2">Customer Lifetime Value analysis showing distribution and relationship with recency, frequency, and monetary factors.</figcaption>
            </div>
            <div class="row mt-4">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <h5>Average CLV by Segment</h5>
                    <table class="table table-bordered">
                        <thead class="table-light">
                            <tr>
                                <th>Segment</th>
                                <th>1-Year CLV</th>
                                <th>3-Year CLV</th>
                            </tr>
                        </thead>
                        <tbody>
                            <tr>
                                <td>VIP Customers</td>
                                <td>$842</td>
                                <td>$2,105</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td>Loyal Customers</td>
                                <td>$485</td>
                                <td>$1,213</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td>New Potential</td>
                                <td>$328</td>
                                <td>$820</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td>Dormant High Value</td>
                                <td>$136</td>
                                <td>$340</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td>Occasional Customers</td>
                                <td>$98</td>
                                <td>$245</td>
                            </tr>
                        </tbody>
                    </table>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <h5>Key CLV Insights</h5>
                    <ul>
                        <li>VIP customers represent 15% of the customer base but account for 42% of predicted future revenue</li>
                        <li>Reactivating dormant high-value customers offers significant ROI potential</li>
                        <li>New customers show promising lifetime value when effectively nurtured</li>
                        <li>Purchase frequency is the strongest predictor of high lifetime value</li>
                        <li>Customer acquisition cost should be differentiated by predicted segment CLV</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
<!-- Segment Strategies Section -->
<section class="container mb-5">
    <h2 class="section-title">Segment Strategies</h2>
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
            <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h4 class="card-title">VIP Customers</h4>
                    <p class="text-muted mb-3">15% of customers, 42% of revenue</p>
                    <h5>Characteristics</h5>
                    <ul>
                        <li>High purchase frequency (5+ orders/year)</li>
                        <li>High average order value ($120+)</li>
                        <li>Recent purchases (within 30 days)</li>
                        <li>Broad category exploration</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
            <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h4 class="card-title">Loyal Customers</h4>
                    <p class="text-muted mb-3">22% of customers, 28% of revenue</p>
                    <h5>Characteristics</h5>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Regular purchase frequency (3-4 orders/year)</li>
                        <li>Moderate average order value ($75-120)</li>
                        <li>Consistent category preferences</li>
                        <li>Price-sensitive but loyal</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
            <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h4 class="card-title">Dormant High Value</h4>
                    <p class="text-muted mb-3">12% of customers, 8% of revenue</p>
                    <h5>Characteristics</h5>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Previously frequent purchasers</li>
                        <li>No purchases in 60+ days</li>
                        <li>Historically high CLV</li>
                        <li>Often multi-category shoppers</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Conclusions Section -->
<section class="container mb-5">
    <h2 class="section-title">Business Impact & Recommendations</h2>
    <div class="card border-0 shadow">
        <div class="card-body">
            <h4 class="mb-3">Key Business Insights</h4>
            <ol>
                <li><strong>Segment-Based Strategy:</strong> The analysis revealed six distinct customer segments, each requiring different marketing approaches and retention strategies.</li>
                <li><strong>High-Value Customer Focus:</strong> VIP and Loyal customers represent 37% of the customer base but account for 70% of revenue, justifying premium retention efforts.</li>
                <li><strong>Reactivation Opportunity:</strong> Dormant high-value customers represent a $1.2M revenue opportunity if effectively reactivated.</li>
                <li><strong>Product Associations:</strong> Strong product associations were identified that can drive bundling strategies and increase average order value.</li>
                <li><strong>Customer Lifecycle Management:</strong> Cohort analysis revealed critical drop-off points where intervention is most effective.</li>
            </ol>
            
            
            <h4 class="mb-3 mt-4">Expected Results</h4>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="card bg-light">
                        <div class="card-body text-center">
                            <h5 class="card-title">Revenue Increase</h5>
                            <p class="display-4">18%</p>
                            <p class="card-text">Projected annual revenue growth from implementing segment-based strategies</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="card bg-light">
                        <div class="card-body text-center">
                            <h5 class="card-title">Customer Retention</h5>
                            <p class="display-4">+12%</p>
                            <p class="card-text">Expected improvement in customer retention rate</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="card bg-light">
                        <div class="card-body text-center">
                            <h5 class="card-title">Average Order Value</h5>
                            <p class="display-4">+24%</p>
                            <p class="card-text">Projected increase in average order value from cross-selling and bundling</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
